                  <h3 class="top-articles__item-title">
                    
                    <a class="top-articles__item-link" href="/news/2020-06-04/police-receive-hundreds-of-calls-and-emails-after-new-madeleine-mccann-appeal/">Madeleine McCann: Hundreds respond to new appeal</a>
                  </h3>

                      <p class="top-articles__item-summary">
                        <p>Scotland Yard has received hundreds of emails and calls from the public after urging people to come forward.</p>

<p>German prosecutors believe Madeleine is dead and are investigating a convicted child sex predator on suspicion of her murder.</p>

                      </p>

                    <ol class="top-articles__item-links">
                        <li class="top-articles__item-links__item">
                          <a href="https://www.itv.com/news/2020-06-04/madeleine-mccann-german-suspect-what-do-we-know-about-the-suspect-identified/">What do we know about suspect in Madeleine disappearance?</a>
